title: Ab-Soul Announces "YMF" Tour With Little Simz
text:
Home > Music > Ab-Soul Announces "YMF" Tour With Little Simz Ab-Soul Announces "YMF" Tour With Little Simz 0 0 Posted by Trevor Smith , Mar 8, 2017 at 05:24pm Soulo shares dates in support of "Do What Thou Wilt." 
After dropping his Do What Thou Wilt LP last December, Ab-Soul is ready to head out on tour in support of the project. Soulo has announced the YMF tour, named after the closing track on the project, on Twitter today. 
The North American tour kicks off April 12th in Vancouver, BC, before taking the TDE rapper through major cities like Houston, Atlanta, New York, Philadelphia, Toronto, Chicago, and L.A., closing off June 27th in Sanata Ana, CA. 
UK rapper Little Simz will serve as the supporting act on select dates. Soul's message to the fans along with the dates: "Only cause I Care about ya." 
View the full schedule below. Only cause I care about ya... pic.twitter.com/MrfX2661WN
